node.text:
Here’s to the groundwork behind the race in the sky. The new #LandRover #DEFENDER and all the teams of @redbullxalps, capable of great things together. Tap the link in our bio to explore the defender.

#TeamDefender #AboveAndBeyond #Adventure #AdventureRace #RedBullXAlps #Paragliding #Alps

node.title: New DEFENDER and the Red Bull X-Alps - Capable of Great Things together

node.text:
From Lake Bennett to the Bering Sea and across 2000 miles of wildlife, rough waters and more, former special forces operator and adventurer @jason_carl_fox and fellow adventurer Sean Johnson took on an epic unsupported expedition along the length of the Yukon River by Kayak. Learn more about their incredible journey in this video. #AboveAndBeyondStories 

#Adventure #Adventurer #Expedition #Yukon #EnduranceSport #Kayaking #Kayak

node.title: Above and Beyond Stories – Traversing the Yukon River with Jason Fox

node.text:
Walking in the footsteps of 'Captain Scott’, @polarben set out to break the world record for the longest human-powered polar journey in history on a 1,795-mile trek to the South Pole while facing intense cold, altitude and weakened by half-rations. Learn about surviving on the edge in his video, and share your questions for Ben in his upcoming interview in the comments. #AboveAndBeyondStories 

#Livestream #Adventure #Adventurer #Expedition #Polar #Antarctic #EnduranceSport #Arctic

Here’s to the groundwork behind the race in the sky. The new #LandRover #DEFENDER and all the teams of @redbullxalps, capable of great things together. Tap the link in our bio to explore the defender.

#TeamDefender #AboveAndBeyond #Adventure #AdventureRace #RedBullXAlps #Paragliding #Alps

node.text:
Built for the toughest demands, the new #DEFENDER's confident capability was key to @theturnertwiins drive to explore Scotland, from shifting sands to windswept mountains and with storage for surfboards, kiteboards, parachutes and more. Configure yours via the link in our bio. 

📷 @alexanderrhind #TeamDefender #NewDefender #Adventure #Together #Explore #Outdoors #Scotland #Travel #Mountains #Hillside #Coast #Beach #KiteBoarding #Kites

node.text:
Driving forwards in the vanguard of a new era of exploration, we are proud to have played our part in our partner @virgingalactic's first fully-crewed spaceflight last weekend, embodying our #AboveAndBeyond spirit on an out-of-this-world journey. Watch more via the link in our bio.

@landroversv #SV #SpecialVehicleOperations #Defender #NewDefender #TeamDefender #RangeRover #AstronautEdition #Space #Spaceflight #Spaceship #VirginGalactic

node.text:
Adventure athletes and #LandRover fans @theturnertwiins made waves on a trip to the west coast of Scotland in the new #DEFENDER. Its extraordinary capability and clever accessories helped them find the best off-grid locations for a surfing adventure. Configure yours via the link in our bio. 

📷 @alexanderrhind #TeamDefender #NewDefender #Coast #Adventure #Together #Explore #Outdoors #Beach #Surfing #Surf #Scotland #Travel #Staycation
